column3: Rewards for the “Feast” will be earned based on a participant's tier standing at the end of each season.
Exclusive bonuses will also be awarded to the highest-ranked participants, so sharpen your blades, dust off your staves, and make ready for battle.
Make the most of the current preseason period to hone your skills, and aim to claim the choicest prizes once the official first season begins!

Season One is now underway!
Rewards will become available once the season has ended.
Season One rankings can be checked on the Lodestone.
